name: MBI Effective End Date
description: The date that an Medicare Beneficiary Identifier became inactive. In cases where the MBI has changed for a patient, this date will be supplied. This date will be empty if the MBI in question is the current MBI.

fhirMapping.derived: If this field is not populated for a MedicareBeneficiaryIdHistory record then that record will not be added as an Historic MBI in the patient.identifier[N].
